spec_data.Name: qtcurve
spec_data.Description:
QtCurve is a desktop theme for the GTK+ and Qt widget toolkits,
allowing users to achieve a uniform look between these widget toolkits.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 27 Feb 2017 06:55:09 AM EST, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A set of widget styles for GTK+ and Qt widget toolkits
